================================Legacy Loan Calculator===========================
Build Instructions
bash
g++ -std=c++11 -Isrc src/main.cpp src/Loan.cpp -o calc.exe
g++ -std=c++11 -Isrc src/Loan.cpp test/simple_test.cpp -o test_calc.exe
Usage
Run the calculator:

bash
./calc.exe
Then enter:

Loan amount: 100000

Interest rate: 12

Years: 10

Run Tests
bash
./test_calc.exe
Project Structure
text
src/main.cpp - Main calculator
src/Loan.h - Loan class header
src/Loan.cpp - Loan class implementation
test/simple_test.cpp - Test cases
config.txt - Configuration file

==============Features
Calculate total loan amount

Calculate total interest

Calculate monthly payments

Input validation

Unit tests for normal EMI, invalid input, and large numbers
